The rock paper scissors game of DLsite RJ01272755 is difficult.
I make a code to solve that.

Solution:

Turn 1
Player deal paper, PC deal scissors

Turn 2
Player deal scissors, PC deal rock

Turn 3
Use demolition magic to remove one scissors from PC
Player deal paper, PC deal scissors

Turn 4
Use hunai-san magic (船井)
Player deal scissors, PC deal paper
1 win

Turn 5
Use exchange magic, give away 2 rock, take in 2 paper
Player deal paper, PC deal rock
2 win

Turn 6
Player deal paper, PC deal rock
3 win

Turn 7
Player deal paper, PC deal rock
4 win

Turn 8
Use hypnosis magic
Player deal scissors, PC deal rock
5 win

Turn 9
Use truce magic, add scissors
Player deal rock, PC deal scissors
6 win
